<paragraph id="IAS40_61" principles="yes"><paranum>61</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 40"/><data name="paranum" value="61"/></prolog><body><variant base="SL46591659" id="IAS40_61_V2">       <p id="IAS40_P0224">If an <xref base="SL46590609" href="IAS40_5.dita#IAS40_5/IAS40_P0055">owner&#x2011;occupied property<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0279"/></ph></xref> becomes an <xref base="SL46590595" href="IAS40_5.dita#IAS40_5/IAS40_P0050">investment property<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0206"/></ph></xref> that will be carried at <xref base="SL46590585" href="IAS40_5.dita#IAS40_5/IAS40_P0046">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref>, an entity shall apply <xref base="F46591663" href="../IAS16.ditamap" id="IAS40_X0297">IAS 16</xref> for owned property and <xref base="F46976560" href="../ifrs16/IFRS16_TOC.dita#IFRS16_TOC0001" id="IAS40_X0298">IFRS 16</xref> for property held by a lessee as a right-of-use asset up to the date of         change in use. The entity shall treat any difference at that date between the <xref base="SL46590576" href="IAS40_5.dita#IAS40_5/IAS40_P0044">carrying amount<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0027"/></ph></xref> of the property in         accordance with <xref base="F46591665" href="../IAS16.ditamap" id="IAS40_X0299">IAS 16</xref> or IFRS 16 and its fair value in the same way as a revaluation in         accordance with <xref base="F46591666" href="../IAS16.ditamap" id="IAS40_X0300">IAS 16</xref>.  </p>            </variant></body></paragraph>